        "reponse": "<p>\\(\\cos(\\alpha + \\beta) = \\cos\\alpha \\cos\\beta - \\sin\\alpha \\sin\\beta = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} \\times \\frac{1}{2} - \\frac{1}{2} \\times \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{4} - \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{4} = 0\\)</p><p>\\(\\sin(\\alpha + \\beta) = \\sin\\alpha \\cos\\beta + \\cos\\alpha \\sin\\beta = \\frac{1}{2} \\times \\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} \\times \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} = \\frac{1}{4} + \\frac{3}{4} = 1\\)</p>",
